00:19.487 --> 00:23.847
<b>If we kill a devil that a civilian hunter has already engaged, 
we're guilty of interfering in their business.</b>

00:24.197 --> 00:26.487
<b>Normally, you would be arrested.</b>

00:27.227 --> 00:31.897
<b>You need to think before you act, Power.</b>

00:31.897 --> 00:32.917
<b>And you, Denji.</b>

00:32.917 --> 00:34.737
<b>You need to keep her in check.</b>

00:34.737 --> 00:36.727
<b>What? <i>Me</i>?</b>

00:37.007 --> 00:40.697
<b>Before she became a fiend, Power was the Blood Devil.</b>

00:40.697 --> 00:43.597
<b>So fighting using blood is her forte,</b>

00:44.117 --> 00:46.487
<b>but it also makes her rather excitable.</b>

00:46.977 --> 00:49.737
<b>Perhaps she's not suited to being a devil hunter after all.</b>

00:50.047 --> 00:50.747
<b>Thi—</b>

00:51.147 --> 00:54.487
<b>Th-This guy told me to kill it!</b>

00:54.487 --> 00:57.167
<b>What?! How can you just lie like that?!</b>

00:57.167 --> 00:59.087
<b>You're so full of shit!</b>

00:59.087 --> 01:00.707
<b>I am not!</b>

01:00.707 --> 01:04.167
<b>He told me to! This human told me to kill the devil!</b>

01:04.167 --> 01:05.007
<b>It's the truth!</b>

01:05.007 --> 01:06.317
<b>Yikes!</b>

01:06.317 --> 01:06.967
<b>What the...?</b>

01:07.357 --> 01:10.217
<b>Makima, this devil's a straight-up liar!</b>

01:10.587 --> 01:12.077
<b>She should be arrested!</b>

01:12.077 --> 01:14.437
<b>You're under arrest for false whatchamacallit!</b>

01:14.437 --> 01:16.727
<b>Don't listen to him! He told me to do it!</b>

01:17.137 --> 01:18.917
<b>Devils cannot lie!</b>

01:18.917 --> 01:20.647
<b>Only humans lie!</b>

01:20.647 --> 01:22.607
<b>Yeah, right!</b>

01:22.607 --> 01:24.517
<b>You're living proof they can, bozo!</b>

01:24.517 --> 01:26.127
<b>You lying dipshit!</b>

01:26.127 --> 01:28.537
<b>Humans are dirty liars!</b>

01:28.537 --> 01:30.877
<b>I only did what I was told!</b>

01:30.877 --> 01:33.357
<b>Drop the act! Who do you think you are?!</b>

01:33.357 --> 01:34.497
<b>It's so cringe!</b>

01:34.957 --> 01:36.497
<b>Can you settle down for a minute?</b>

01:39.097 --> 01:40.917
<b>I—I can.</b>

01:40.917 --> 01:41.507
<b>Huh?</b>

01:43.597 --> 01:46.127
<b>Good girl, Power.</b>

01:46.127 --> 01:50.147
<b>Really, I couldn't care less which of you is to blame.</b>

01:50.147 --> 01:52.887
<b>All I want is to see you two producing results as a team.</b>

01:53.657 --> 01:56.057
<b>Can you do that for me?</b>

01:56.347 --> 01:58.987
<b>We—W-We will!</b>

