02:25.717 --> 02:29.107
<b><i>Maybe this ain't the best time 
to be focused on touching her boobs.</i></b>

02:46.377 --> 02:50.807
<b>Y'know, drinking a soda used to be something I could only dream about.</b>

02:51.987 --> 02:53.987
<b>But if we keep screwing up,</b>

02:54.627 --> 02:57.607
<b>not getting to drink soda anymore would be the least of my worries.</b>

02:58.837 --> 03:02.447
<b>Still, that doesn't mean I can work with a liar.</b>

03:04.617 --> 03:07.507
<b>I only get along with cats.</b>

03:09.127 --> 03:11.287
<b>I hate humans.</b>

03:11.287 --> 03:14.197
<b>Not because they did something to me.</b>

03:14.197 --> 03:16.717
<b>It's just something devils feel instinctively.</b>

03:17.067 --> 03:19.387
<b>And I hate devils too.</b>

03:19.387 --> 03:22.937
<b>Because one of them kidnapped my pet, Meowy.</b>

03:24.607 --> 03:29.157
<b>Before I could Meowy get back, Makima caught me.</b>

03:29.727 --> 03:33.947
<b>Meowy might already be dead, but I cannot give up hope.</b>

03:34.297 --> 03:37.117
<b>I'd do anything to get Meowy back from that devil.</b>

03:37.117 --> 03:39.677
<b>Even work with humans.</b>

03:40.317 --> 03:43.957
<b>I doubt you'd understand why I'd go to such great lengths for a cat.</b>

03:44.597 --> 03:46.207
<b>A cat?</b>

03:46.207 --> 03:48.417
<b>Yeah, that's dumb.</b>

03:48.417 --> 03:51.997
<b>Though, I reckon I'd do anything 
to be able to feel up a chick's boobs.</b>

03:53.527 --> 03:56.847
<b>I knew I wouldn't be able 
to see eye-to-eye with a human.</b>

03:57.147 --> 03:57.957
<b>Hmm...</b>

03:58.677 --> 03:59.757
<b>But...</b>

04:00.397 --> 04:03.347
<b>If we were talking about a dog, I think I'd get you.</b>

04:05.777 --> 04:08.627
<b>What if I said, if you can get my Meowy back,</b>

04:08.627 --> 04:10.647
<b>I'll let you feel up <i>my</i> boobs?</b>

04:16.327 --> 04:17.777
<b>That fuckin' devil!</b>

04:18.147 --> 04:18.667
<b>Oh?</b>

04:18.667 --> 04:21.917
<b>Who does he think he is, kidnapping a cat?!</b>

04:22.167 --> 04:22.917
<b>Oh!</b>

04:22.917 --> 04:25.737
<b>Not on my watch!</b>

04:25.737 --> 04:26.667
<b>Oh!</b>

04:27.817 --> 04:29.667
<b>As a devil hunter, I won't let this slide!</b>

04:29.967 --> 04:30.927
<b>Oh!</b>

04:30.927 --> 04:35.327
<b>I'm gonna slaughter that devil!</b>

04:41.067 --> 04:43.987
<b>Leave for the fiend Power is approved.</b>

04:43.307 --> 04:44.807
<b>Approval</b>

04:43.307 --> 04:44.807
m 1305 681 l 1389 666 1368 639 1281 654

04:45.557 --> 04:47.807
<b>Make sure she's back by 5 P.M.</b>

04:48.407 --> 04:50.957
<b>You're not allowed to go out on your own?</b>

04:50.957 --> 04:54.537
<b>Nope. I've been dying of boredom in here all this time.</b>

05:07.867 --> 05:11.257
<b>I know where to find the devil that kidnapped Meowy.</b>

05:11.257 --> 05:13.957
<b>The problem is... only <i>you</i> can fight him.</b>

05:15.477 --> 05:20.297
<b>As soon as he sees me, 
he'll use Meowy as a shield.</b>

05:21.077 --> 05:23.307
<b>And that would be checkmate.</b>

05:27.117 --> 05:30.017
<b>I also had a pet. A devil called Pochita.</b>

05:30.667 --> 05:34.147
<b>I can't pet him any more, but that's okay.</b>

05:35.257 --> 05:37.827
<b>He still lives here, inside of me.</b>

05:37.827 --> 05:39.957
<b>Humans really are so foolish.</b>

05:39.957 --> 05:40.987
<b>What?</b>

05:41.257 --> 05:44.317
<b>In essence, you're saying that Pochita is dead, correct?</b>

05:44.317 --> 05:46.067
<b>What's dead is gone.</b>

05:46.067 --> 05:48.247
<b>Nonsense like "he's still alive in my heart"</b>

05:48.247 --> 05:50.597
<b>is nothing but a pitiful attempt at self-consolation.</b>

05:57.917 --> 05:59.477
<b>Yeah, yeah.</b>

05:59.477 --> 06:00.797
<b>Guess you're right.</b>

06:06.677 --> 06:09.307
<b><i>I don't think I'm gonna get along with her.</i></b>

06:10.007 --> 06:11.027
<b><i>Ever.</i></b>

06:19.077 --> 06:24.197
<b>Because of what happened in the US, 
the hardliners in the USSR are gaining influence.</b>

06:24.547 --> 06:28.567
<b>There are also rumors of devils being used for military purposes.</b>

06:28.807 --> 06:33.987
<b>We'd like to keep Japan's enemies limited to <i>just</i> the devils.</b>

06:33.987 --> 06:38.577
<b>Makima, how goes the training of the dogs in that unit of yours?</b>

06:38.947 --> 06:42.117
<b>I have one that seems promising</b>

06:42.117 --> 06:43.757
<b>and one that is rather interesting.</b>

06:44.237 --> 06:45.717
<b>One that's interesting?</b>

06:46.037 --> 06:47.877
<b>The latest pup I picked up.</b>

