<b>In regard to the subject of this document, I have the following to report:</b>

06:47.927 --> 06:48.017
<b>Tokyo, Nerima, Seibu Railway Nerima Station, near the South entrance</b>

06:47.927 --> 06:48.017
<b>Power (fiend), devil hunter from the Fourth Special Anti-Devil Division of the Public Safety Bureau</b>

06:47.927 --> 06:48.017
<b>Asagi Kounosuke (human), civilian devil hunter</b>

06:47.927 --> 06:48.017
<b>Devil hunters Power and Denji from the Fourth Special Anti-Devil Division of the Public Safety Bureau were on patrol near Nerima Station, when Power reacted to the smell of blood and went towards it alone.


The Sea Cucumber Devil had appeared on the street near the southern entrance of Nerima Station and Power, who had rushed to the location, killed it using her special weapon.


At the time Power noticed the Sea Cucumber Devil, a civilian devil hunter (Asagi) had already started to secure it. He had established a perimeter and evacuated all civilians, and was in the process of requesting backup from a nearby phone box.


After Denji reached the location he contacted [REDACTED] and reported the details of the incident. The Sea Cucumber Devil is dead, Asagi, Power, and Denji were unhurt.</b>

06:47.927 --> 06:48.017
<b>Asagi settlement money is still being negotiated.
After having showed signs of repentance. Denji was also reprimanded
That is all.</b>

