<b>Devil hunters Power and Denji from the Fourth Special Anti-Devil Division of the Public Safety Bureau were on patrol near Nerima Station, when Power reacted to the smell of blood and went towards it alone.


The Sea Cucumber Devil had appeared on the street near the southern entrance of Nerima Station and Power, who had rushed to the location, killed it using her special weapon.


At the time Power noticed the Sea Cucumber Devil, a civilian devil hunter (Asagi) had already started to secure it. He had established a perimeter and evacuated all civilians, and was in the process of requesting backup from a nearby phone box.


