06:48.717 --> 06:49.097
<b>Resolution</b>

06:49.667 --> 06:52.237
<b>Remember, your job is to train these dogs,</b>

06:52.237 --> 06:54.157
<b>and then make use of them.</b>

06:54.157 --> 06:57.227
<b>It <i>isn't</i> to get attached to them.</b>

07:12.437 --> 07:15.457
<b>Denji isn't interesting. He's just unpleasant.</b>

07:17.387 --> 07:19.787
<b>Why do you have such high hopes for him?</b>

07:34.787 --> 07:38.517
<b>Every devil is born with a name.</b>

07:38.927 --> 07:41.907
<b>The more feared that name is,</b>

07:41.907 --> 07:45.027
<b>the more powerful the devil is said to be.</b>

07:45.337 --> 07:49.727
<b>Take coffee, for example. It's hard to imagine "coffee" evoking fear in most people.</b>

07:49.727 --> 07:53.027
<b>So if there was a Coffee Devil, 
it would likely be rather weak.</b>

07:53.657 --> 07:56.927
<b>But what about a Car Devil, then?</b>

07:57.487 --> 08:00.427
<b>People might imagine themselves getting run over and dying,</b>

08:00.427 --> 08:01.587
<b>so it could be strong.</b>

08:03.837 --> 08:07.297
<b>Denji can turn into the Chainsaw Devil.</b>

08:09.297 --> 08:11.447
<b>I think that's quite interesting.</b>

08:15.447 --> 08:18.597
<b>Maybe you're right, but I still don't think he can be useful.</b>

08:20.507 --> 08:24.717
<b>Everyone in the Bureau has a goal or strong conviction.</b>

08:24.717 --> 08:26.007
<b>But Denji?</b>

08:26.007 --> 08:28.867
<b>He said all he wants is to live a laid-back life.</b>

08:29.507 --> 08:31.937
<b>He isn't fit for the Bureau.</b>

08:31.937 --> 08:35.377
<b>And even worse, he thinks you can become friends with devils.</b>

08:36.387 --> 08:38.377
<b>He's still a kid.</b>

08:38.677 --> 08:39.467
<b>A brat.</b>

08:53.237 --> 08:54.887
<b>That's the house!</b>

08:55.767 --> 08:58.087
<b>Meowy and the devil are in there.</b>

08:59.557 --> 09:00.637
<b>Right.</b>

09:01.287 --> 09:03.157
<b>Let's do this thing.</b>

09:10.747 --> 09:13.977
<b>I don't really wanna bust out the chainsaws 'cause I'll lose a lot of blood.</b>

09:14.617 --> 09:16.997
<b>What? Chainsaws?</b>

09:16.997 --> 09:20.097
<b>Yup, I can turn my body into chainsaws.</b>

09:20.097 --> 09:22.627
<b>I am yet to understand the humor of humans.</b>

09:27.107 --> 09:27.927
<b>Huh?</b>

09:27.927 --> 09:29.427
<b>What is it?</b>

09:29.877 --> 09:33.437
<b>Didn't you say he'd use your cat as a shield if you showed yourself?</b>

09:34.017 --> 09:36.547
<b>Probably not a good idea for you to come this close, then.</b>

09:36.837 --> 09:40.057
<b>Oh, right. That's the story I told you.</b>

09:40.317 --> 09:41.557
<b>Story?</b>

09:41.797 --> 09:44.317
<b>Just a slip of the tongue.</b>

09:59.197 --> 10:00.747
<b>You're a fool.</b>

10:01.197 --> 10:03.427
<b>But you have good instincts.</b>

10:28.137 --> 10:32.807
<b>You kept me waiting for quite some time, Blood Devil.</b>

10:32.807 --> 10:35.487
<b>I thought you had run away.</b>

10:35.777 --> 10:37.547
<b>Spare me your complaints.</b>

10:37.547 --> 10:39.997
<b>Getting out was not easy.</b>

10:40.607 --> 10:44.437
<b>I brought you a human, as you requested, Bat.</b>

10:48.277 --> 10:50.707
<b>I haven't had anything to eat in a while.</b>

10:51.077 --> 10:52.787
<b>A young male, I see.</b>

10:52.787 --> 10:56.097
<b>His blood should be rather invigorating.</b>

11:01.767 --> 11:05.097
<b>Look at this wound on my arm, human.</b>

11:05.097 --> 11:08.107
<b>Your kind gave me this...</b>

11:08.107 --> 11:13.567
<b>An irritating wound that forces me to hide here!</b>

11:14.327 --> 11:16.317
<b>Like I give a shit, dumbass.</b>

11:16.317 --> 11:18.327
<b>No barking, lunch!</b>

11:18.787 --> 11:24.787
<b>Humans caused this wound, 
and now your human blood will heal it.</b>

11:30.997 --> 11:32.757
<b>Disgusting!</b>

11:34.997 --> 11:40.177
<b>I've been restored by this putrid blood!</b>

11:44.677 --> 11:47.657
<b>Such a foul taste!</b>

11:47.657 --> 11:51.187
<b>I'll need another human to wash it away!</b>

11:59.327 --> 12:02.197
<b><i>You want to be friends with them?{ep02@16:34}</i></b>

12:07.417 --> 12:11.347
<b>You actually believed my story.</b>

12:14.107 --> 12:17.027
<b>Humans really are so foolish.</b>

12:24.687 --> 12:26.847
<b>The stench of cigarettes,</b>

12:27.287 --> 12:30.107
<b>make-up, and drugs.</b>

12:30.107 --> 12:30.967
<b>Seriously?</b>

12:30.967 --> 12:31.977
<b>Crazy, right?</b>

12:33.717 --> 12:36.357
<b>Now, <i>there's</i> a smell I like.</b>

12:36.857 --> 12:39.867
<b>I'll cleanse my palate with some children.</b>

12:40.687 --> 12:42.107
<b>Hey, Bat Devil!</b>

12:42.107 --> 12:43.367
<b>Huh?</b>

12:43.877 --> 12:46.447
<b>I brought you a human as promised.</b>

12:46.877 --> 12:48.697
<b>Return Meowy to me.</b>

12:49.237 --> 12:51.407
<b>Huh?</b>

12:51.407 --> 12:55.457
<b>Oh, yes. That was our agreement, wasn't it?</b>

12:59.547 --> 13:00.467
<b>Meowy!</b>

13:00.467 --> 13:05.967
<b>But I haven't punished you for bringing me such revolting blood yet.</b>

13:10.437 --> 13:11.577
<b>Meowy...</b>

13:12.027 --> 13:13.307
<b>Meowy.</b>

13:13.667 --> 13:15.667
<b>That's your name now.</b>

13:15.667 --> 13:18.567
<b>You smell tasty for a cat.</b>

13:23.077 --> 13:26.077
<b>You're pretty scrawny.</b>

13:26.597 --> 13:29.727
<b>I'll fatten you up a bit before I eat you.</b>

13:39.797 --> 13:42.217
<b>Hurry up and grow.</b>

13:42.477 --> 13:45.697
<b>I cannot wait until I can kill you.</b>

13:54.937 --> 13:58.667
<b>I've killed every being who has met my gaze.</b>

14:00.187 --> 14:04.267
<b>Hearing a voice that isn't screaming feels curious.</b>

14:05.817 --> 14:07.197
<b>Curious...</b>

14:13.997 --> 14:15.917
<b>Blood Devil.</b>

14:18.087 --> 14:20.167
<b>I need blood.</b>

14:20.757 --> 14:23.947
<b>If you do not wish for this cat to die,</b>

14:23.947 --> 14:26.927
<b>then bring me a human.</b>

14:44.207 --> 14:47.187
<b>You said that you can no longer pet Pochita.</b>

14:49.057 --> 14:51.297
<b>Now I know how you feel.</b>

14:52.707 --> 14:54.407
<b>It's a horrible feeling.</b>

15:03.027 --> 15:04.357
<b>Disgusting!</b>

15:04.357 --> 15:07.027
<b>Why is all this blood <i>so</i> disgusting?!</b>

15:11.437 --> 15:13.937
<b>My mouth feels so gross!</b>

15:14.397 --> 15:17.187
<b>I need to rinse it out with the blood of a child.</b>

15:22.247 --> 15:26.447
<b>And after, as a starter, I'll have a virgin girl.</b>

15:26.757 --> 15:29.447
<b>For the main course, I'll take a plump man.</b>

15:29.847 --> 15:32.677
<b>And for dessert, a pregnant woman.</b>

15:36.457 --> 15:39.257
<b>Gimme back my boobs!</b>

15:39.257 --> 15:43.257
<b>You're drinking my blood?! How foul!</b>

15:43.257 --> 15:46.737
<b>I don't even want your blood!</b>

15:49.327 --> 15:51.607
<b><i>I remember one time Pochita disappeared.</i></b>

15:52.857 --> 15:55.267
<b><i>I woke up, and he wasn't there.</i></b>

15:55.977 --> 15:58.347
<b><i>I looked all over town, but I couldn't find him.</i></b>

15:59.987 --> 16:02.277
<b><i>I thought he'd been eaten by a devil.</i></b>

16:04.417 --> 16:08.447
<b><i>But when I got home, Pochita was sitting there, 
waiting for me with tears in his eyes.</i></b>

16:09.817 --> 16:12.777
<b><i>That night, I was filled with relief 
and fell asleep holding him.</i></b>

16:15.127 --> 16:17.457
<b><i>She had her Meowy kidnapped by a devil.</i></b>

16:18.957 --> 16:21.337
<b><i>I wonder how she felt when she tried to sleep that night.</i></b>

16:34.017 --> 16:36.717
<b>You're a devil?!</b>

17:02.337 --> 17:04.967
<b>Are you stupid?! You wanna get eaten?!</b>

17:07.557 --> 17:10.047
<b>You let a human get away?</b>

17:10.627 --> 17:14.237
<b>You're a devil! What are you trying to achieve here?</b>

17:15.997 --> 17:18.137
<b>I'm gonna split your belly open,</b>

17:18.137 --> 17:20.757
<b>and then I'm gonna feel up those boobs!</b>

18:02.977 --> 18:04.017
<b>Get outta here already!</b>

18:13.767 --> 18:16.787
<b>If you're trying to save humans,</b>

18:19.417 --> 18:22.037
<b>then let's see you cut through this!</b>

18:25.947 --> 18:27.917
<b>I can retract my chainsaws?!</b>

18:27.917 --> 18:30.417
<b>That strength is well beyond your looks!</b>

18:30.417 --> 18:33.697
<b>Why waste it on saving a pitiful human?</b>

18:35.327 --> 18:37.677
<b>Who said I'm trying to save him?</b>

18:37.677 --> 18:38.557
<b>Huh?</b>

18:39.157 --> 18:42.807
<b>Like I give a shit</b>

18:43.717 --> 18:45.307
<b>about some dude's life!</b>

19:16.417 --> 19:18.727
<b>First, I need to recover.</b>

19:18.727 --> 19:21.847
<b>This cigarette-smelling blood will have to do.</b>

19:23.617 --> 19:24.457
<b>Huh?</b>

19:25.327 --> 19:28.277
<b>How are you alive?</b>

19:30.477 --> 19:34.107
<b>I've been through so much shit</b>

19:35.517 --> 19:38.037
<b>and put up with so much bullshit!</b>

19:40.337 --> 19:43.547
<b>And I still haven't...</b>

19:43.547 --> 19:49.197
<b>even touched a chick's boobs!</b>

20:02.877 --> 20:05.977
<b>S-Stay away!</b>

